snippet.title: Aquaman (2018) "Fun on Set with Jason Momoa and Amber Heard" Featurette [Digital Blu Ray DVD]
snippet.description:
Arthur Curry, the human-born heir to the underwater kingdom of Atlantis, goes on a quest to prevent a war between the worlds of ocean and land.

Director: James Wan
Writers: David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick (screenplay by), Will Beall (screenplay by) 
Stars: Jason Momoa, Amber Heard, Willem Dafoe
